<Routine Name="tank_control_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[储液罐液位控制流程。
液位过高过低报警。
液位过高时关闭进液阀，防止储液罐过满；
液位过低时关闭出液阀，防止计量泵空吸。]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_1,PAC_tank_level_8LT01,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_1,PAC_level_low_alarm_1,VE_PAC_05_actuate,VE_PAC_07_actuate);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#PAC池]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_2,PAC_tank_level_8LT02,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_2,PAC_level_low_alarm_2,VE_PAC_06_actuate,VE_PAC_08_actuate);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_3,PAC_tank_level_8LT03,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_3,PAC_level_low_alarm_3,temp_1,VE_PAC_09_actuate);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_4,PAC_tank_level_8LT04,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_4,PAC_level_low_alarm_4,temp_2,VE_PAC_10_actuate);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
</Program>
